For Sale or Lease

CBRE is pleased to present for Sale or Lease the ground floor tenancy at unit 5, 38 Colin Street, West Perth. 

Prominently located near the intersection of Colin and Ord Street, 38 Colin presents a modern boutique building with an elevated street exposure and striking appearance.

A short walk to the West Perth caf√© and retail precinct, the building is easily accessible via the freeway and CAT bus system and benefits from nearby amenity provided by the stunning Kings Park.

The existing 113sqm* fit out comprises a waiting area/entry statement, 4 offices, 3 work stations, kitchen, storage & w/c. The 2 allocated car parking bays are located in the basement of the building and are fully secured.

Situated at the North-East corner of the building, the space is well suited to multiple end users including but not limited to a boutique accounting or legal practice, medical/consulting business & mining related services. 

For further information or to arrange an inspection, please contact the exclusive selling and leasing agents CBRE

*approx

Modern three level stand-alone office building with secure ground floor car park. The building has been recently refurbished with new air conditioning, lift and base building finishes throughout. The bathrooms on each floor have also been upgraded to a modern standard.

Located on the corner of Prowse Street and Lucknow Place, the building has a great profile with visibility to Thomas Street. Public transport amenity includes City West Train Station and the CAT bus services within walking distance.

Current availabilities:

Level 3 - 255sqm: Partitioned tenancy incorporating a reception, meeting room, open plan working area, multiple offices and kitchen/bathrooms.

Level 2 - 255sqm: Partitioned tenancy incorporating a training room, boardroom, open plan working area, multiple offices and kitchen/bathrooms. 

Level 1 - Up to 255sqm: Partitioned tenancy incorporating a 10+ offices, training room, boardroom, meeting room and kitchenette/bathrooms.

Whole building can be made available subject to negotiation.

Outgoings: Estimated at $136/sqm for the 2020/21 financial year.

Car Parking: 1 bay per 55sqm of lettable area. 

Shower facilities and bicycle parking available.

Fibre available to the premises.

For any queries, please contact the exclusive agents.

668 Murray Street, West Perth -

Whole Floor Available - Signage Opportunity!

Well presented three level office building refurbished to a good standard throughout, featuring a lower ground floor tenancy, secure car parking area and rear lane access.

The building occupies a high profile location in close proximity to the intersection of Havelock Street and Murray Street.

Lower Ground - 196.90sqm.
Large training room with operable wall, large kitchen/breakout area, male & female bathrooms and shower facilities. 

Level 2 - 326.7sqm.

Whole floor fitted tenancy incorporating a combination of open plan workstations, kitchen, meeting rooms and offices. Potential to split from 250sqm

Low building outgoings estimated at $105/sqm per annum

Secure car parking available.

For any queries, please contact the joint-exclusive agents.

610 Murray Street is a refurbished three level office building with secure basement car parking, occupying a prominent position on the corner of Murray Street and Gordon Street.

The property is well located in close proximity to the West End CBD, close to public transport and access to the freeway North & South.

The Red CAT bus stop is positioned at the front of the property, and the Yellow CAT bus stop is in close proximity on Wellington Street.

GROUND FLOOR: 514sqm - Modern fitout including a reception, staff room, 5 x class rooms, kitchen/assembly hall, study and ablution facilities. The tenant is responsible for conducting all investigations into the existing approvals.

GROUND FLOOR: 355sqm - Fitted space featuring reception area, large boardroom, open plan office space with workstations, kitchen/breakout area. 

Level 1: 437 sqm - Modern tenancy with entry/reception, large boardroom, 10 x perimeter offices, open plan working area, kitchen/breakout, storage and comms. Predominantly furnished tenancy.

Positioned in close proximity to the very popular 'Gordon Street Garage' restaurant and cafe.

Outgoings estimate of $175.82/sqm for the 2021/22 financial year, payable by the lessee.

EOT facilities, including shower facilities and secure bicycle parking.

High parking availability.

Signage opportunities available in this high exposure location!
